Executive Compensation
As President, Chief Operating Officer, Director at PROVIDENCE AND WORCESTER RR, P. Scott Conti  made $263,150 in total compensation.  Of this total $238,479 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $9,712 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $14,959 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2015 fiscal year. 


